fields.value: Replication Materials for "Walking the Walk? Experiments on the Effect of Pledging to Vote on Youth Turnout"

dsDescriptionValue.value: This file contains the data and code necessary to replicate the results published in "Walking the Walk? Experiments on the Effect of Pledging to Vote on Youth Turnout" (Costa, Schaffner, and Prevost 2018). Files beginning with "co_" are used in the replication for the Colorado field experiment and files beginning with "pa_" are used in the replication for the Pennsylvania experiment. See the Stata .do files for the replication code.

publicationCitation.value: Costa, Mia, Brian F. Schaffner, and Alicia Prevost. 2018. "Walking the Walk? Experiments on the Effect of Pledging to Vote on Youth Turnout." PlosOne.
